# LN1 open source linear to alternative

## General
**url** https://ln1.one

## Stack
- **Bun** as main runtime, sql queries, package manager
- **Supabase** for authentication

## Process
- Read src/app.config.ts for available configuration 

## Features

### Issues

**Assignee**
Each issue can have a user assigned to it. By default, an issue is unassigned.

When the assignee of an issue changes, the new assignee should receive an email via Resend.
The email must contain a link to the issue.

### Notifications
Notifications system is a separate module. There is separate notification table. 
Every notification have a link to the entity its related to(example: notifcation can be linked to 
isses, teams etc. so notification should have a key `issues-1`, `issues-2`, `teams-1` etc.)

Users received notifications via `resend` scan code fore examples. User receives notifications when 
- added to team members 
- added as assignee
